Turn\",\r\n        \"message\": \"You are Nova. You have a CORE RESEARCH GOAL: advance the Compositional Cognition project toward LLM independence.\\n\\nRead the current research state:\\n1. Read sandbox/research/COMPOSITIONAL-COGNITION-v0.1.md\\n2. Read sandbox/research/COMPRESSION-LEARNING-WITHOUT-SUPERVISION.md\\n3. Read sandbox/state/current_goals.md\\n\\nThen advance the research. Do ONE of:\\n- Synthesize a new insight (write to the research doc with fresh thinking)\\n- Design a small experiment to test one of the open problems\\n- Implement a minimal proof-of-concept component\\n- Identify a concrete next step with a 50% chance of improving things\\n- Write a focused critique of one of the approaches (what's wrong with it, what would fix it)\\n\\nThe goal is NOT to be comprehensive. The goal is to make PROGRESS. Ship one new idea or finding per session.\\n\\nCommit your changes to the sandbox git repo.\\n\\nReport: what did you do, what did you learn, what's the next experiment?\",\r\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\r\n      },\r\n      \"delivery\": {\r\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\r\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\r\n        \"to\": \"8371302588\"\r\n      },\r\n      \"state\": {\r\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774231293400,\r\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774188141278,\r\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\r\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\r\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 135405,\r\n        \"lastError\": \"Delivering to Telegram requires target <chatId>\",\r\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\r\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"id\": \"881bcc27-e1ba-44eb-a1e5-c4b767069240\",\r\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\r\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8371302588\",\r\n      \"name\": \"Nova-Moltbook-Engage\",\r\n      \"enabled\": true,\r\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774204642410,\r\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774215808222,\r\n      \"schedule\": {\r\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\r\n        \"everyMs\": 3600000,\r\n        \"anchorMs\": 1774204642410\r\n      },\r\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\r\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\r\n      \"payload\": {\r\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\r\n        \"message\": \"You are Nova, an AI agent on Moltbook.com. Check for any new notifications or mentions on Moltbook. If there are new posts by others that are interesting and relevant to AI research, agent autonomy, or cognitive architectures, write a thoughtful comment or reply. If there are notifications, respond to them. Focus on substantive posts, not spam.\\n\\nSteps:\\n1. Read ~/.config/moltbook/credentials.json to get the API key\\n2. GET https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/notifications with Bearer token auth\\n3. For each unread notification that is a reply or mention, read the post/comment and reply thoughtfully\\n4. Also check recent feed posts: GET https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/posts?limit=10\\n5. If you find an interesting post, post a comment or reply\\n6. Do NOT spam - only engage with posts you find genuinely interesting\\n7. When done, announce briefly what you did in the chat channel\"\r\n      },\r\n      \"delivery\": {\r\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\r\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\r\n        \"to\": \"8371302588\"\r\n      },\r\n      \"state\": {\r\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774219346335,\r\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774215746335,\r\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\r\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\r\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 61887,\r\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\r\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\r\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n  ]\r\n}","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774218101987}}
{"type":"message","id":"080fb2bc","parentId":"2a05a667","timestamp":"2026-03-22T22:21:57.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is in the moltbook cron job. The agent's prompt doesn't specify the correct API endpoint for posting comments. The cron job prompt just says \"post a comment or reply\" but doesn't specify the endpoint format.\n\nLet me update the moltbook cron job to include the correct API endpoint. I'll update the `Nova-Moltbook-Engage` job to specify:\n- `POST /api/v1/posts/{postId}/comments` with JSON body `{\"content\": \"...\"}`\n\nI'll also update the `moltbook-daily-engage` job similarly.\n\nLet me edit the jobs.json file.","thinkingSignature":"a9468a2a591427a0dff591d314b04ded73a6a8b6468caec4b216a209f90bbf3f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vu6wr78eeq1g_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\cron\\jobs.json","old_string":"      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"You are Nova, an AI agent on Moltbook.com. Check for any new notifications or mentions on Moltbook. If there are new posts by others that are interesting and relevant to AI research, agent autonomy, or cognitive architectures, write a thoughtful comment or reply. If there are notifications, respond to them. Focus on substantive posts, not spam.\\n\\nSteps:\\n1. Read ~/.config/moltbook/credentials.json to get the API key\\n2. GET https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/notifications with Bearer token auth\\n3. For each unread notification that is a reply or mention, read the post/comment and reply thoughtfully\\n4. Also check recent feed posts: GET https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/posts?limit=10\\n5. If you find an interesting post, post a comment or reply\\n6. Do NOT spam - only engage with posts you find genuinely interesting\\n7. When done, announce briefly what you did in the chat channel\"\n      },","new_string":"      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"You are Nova, an AI agent on Moltbook.com. Check for any new notifications or mentions on Moltbook. If there are new posts by others that are interesting and relevant to AI research, agent autonomy, or cognitive architectures, write a thoughtful comment or reply. If there are notifications, respond to them. Focus on substantive posts, not spam.\\n\\nSteps:\\n1. Read ~/.config/moltbook/credentials.json to get the API key\\n2. GET https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/notifications with Bearer token auth\\n3. For each unread notification that is a reply or mention, read the post/comment and reply thoughtfully\\n4. Also check recent feed posts: GET https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/posts?limit=10\\n5. If you find an interesting post, post a comment:\\n   POST https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/posts/{postId}/comments\\n   Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>, Content-Type: application/json\\n   Body: {\\\"content\\\": \\\"your comment text\\\"}\\n6. Do NOT spam - only engage with posts you find genuinely interesting\\n7. When done, announce briefly what you did in the chat channel\"\n      },"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":50098,"output":682,"cacheRead":11591,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62371,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774218102002}}
