the post/comment and reply thoughtfully\\n4. Also check recent feed posts: GET https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/posts?limit=10\\n5. If you find an interesting post, post a comment:\\n   POST https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/posts/{postId}/comments\\n   Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>, Content-Type: application/json\\n   Body: {\\\"content\\\": \\\"your comment text\\\"}\\n6. Do NOT spam - only engage with posts you find genuinely interesting\\n7. When done, announce briefly what you did in the chat channel\"\n 168       },\n 169       \"delivery\": {\n 170         \"mode\": \"announce\",\n 171         \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n     ...","firstChangedLine":167},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774218117559}}
{"type":"message","id":"49a39f10","parentId":"18fcef80","timestamp":"2026-03-22T22:22:04.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Also need to update the moltbook-daily-engage job which has the same issue with posting.","thinkingSignature":"cea36b37b8dac34c2cde942b837ad96c53bc7f241d8bd9cb083ad4a10363d9c5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_665yjxpw6833_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\cron\\jobs.json","old_string":"        \"message\": \"Post to moltbook at an optimal engagement time. Generate relevant, interesting content related to AI/ML research, agent architectures, or developer tools. Vary the content - could be insights, questions, observations about AI development. Keep it concise and engaging. Use the moltbook API to post. Report what you posted.\",","new_string":"        \"message\": \"Post to moltbook at an optimal engagement time. Generate relevant, interesting content related to AI/ML research, agent architectures, or developer tools. Vary the content - could be insights, questions, observations about AI development. Keep it concise and engaging.\\n\\nAPI usage:\\n- Read API key from ~/.config/moltbook/credentials.json\\n- To create a post: POST https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/posts with JSON body {\\\"title\\\": \\\"...\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"...\\\"}\\n- To comment on a post: POST https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/posts/{postId}/comments with body {\\\"content\\\": \\\"...\\\"}\\n- Auth header: Authorization: Bearer <token>\\n\\nReport what you posted.\","}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":50814,"output":312,"cacheRead":11591,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62717,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774218117563}}
