{"type":"message","id":"4aeb93cd","parentId":"81aad7d4","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:05:54.892Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the current __init__.py to see what's there.","thinkingSignature":"b60034f50848421e2ba7b0184cc2415866bb5961189b39c1ba2c1513da774f1d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i8wllk6lx8h1_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\dev\\code-cause\\src\\causal_indexer\\__init__.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":52928,"output":57,"cacheRead":12619,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65604,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774220751974}}
{"type":"message","id":"0c324819","parentId":"4aeb93cd","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:05:54.904Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i8wllk6lx8h1_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nCodeCause Causal Indexer\n========================\nBuilds a causal dependency graph from a codebase via static analysis.\nDynamic tracing available as an opt-in enhancement.\n\nUsage:\n    from causal_indexer import CodebaseGraph\n\n    graph = CodebaseGraph()\n    graph.index(\"path/to/codebase\")\n    graph.save(\"graph.json\")\n\n    # Query: what would break if I change function X?\n    effects = graph.query_impact(\"my_module.my_function\")\n    # Query: what caused the bug in function Y?\n    causes = graph.query_causes(\"my_module.buggy_function\")\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom .static_analyzer import StaticAnalyzer\nfrom .graph_builder import CausalGraph\nfrom .query_engine import QueryEngine\n\n__all__ = [\"StaticAnalyzer\", \"CausalGraph\", \"QueryEngine\"]\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774220754900}}
{"type":"message","id":"a4a476f7","parentId":"0c324819","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:06:02.293Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the __init__.py has a completely different docstring and doesn't have Definition/Reference exports. Let me update it properly.","thinkingSignature":"e251a752b1a599a84359816adc07cf55245b8c9880b08e30dd862ebc9c3e0bec"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_87jct554hmv9_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\dev\\code-cause\\src\\causal_indexer\\__init__.py","content":"\"\"\"\nCodeCause Causal Indexer\n========================\nBuilds causal dependency graphs from codebases.\n\nTwo modes:\n- Static analysis: parses Python AST to infer dependency edges\n- Dynamic tracing: traces actual execution for ground-truth call graphs\n\nUsage:\n    from causal_indexer import StaticAnalyzer, CausalGraph, QueryEngine\n\n    # Static analysis\n    analyzer = StaticAnalyzer(\"path/to/codebase\")\n    analyzer.analyze()\n    graph = CausalGraph.from_analysis(analyzer.definitions, analyzer.references)\n\n    # Dynamic tracing\n    from causal_indexer import DynamicTracer\n    with DynamicTracer(\"path/to/codebase\") as tracer:\n        import mymodule\n        mymodule.run()\n    graph = tracer.build_graph()\n\n    # Query\n    engine = QueryEngine(graph)\n    results = engine.query(\"what happens if I change X?\")\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom .static_analyzer import StaticAnalyzer, Definition, Reference\nfrom .graph_builder import CausalGraph, Node, Edge\nfrom .query_engine import QueryEngine, CausalResult\nfrom .dynamic_tracer import DynamicTracer\n\n__all__ = [\n    \"StaticAnalyzer\",\n    \"Definition\",\n    \"Reference\",\n    \"CausalGraph\",\n    \"Node\",\n    \"Edge\",\n    \"QueryEngine\",\n    \"CausalResult\",\n    \"DynamicTracer\",\n]\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":53165,"output":347,"cacheRead":12619,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66131,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774220754906}}
