{"type":"message","id":"5f53713c","parentId":"5e0a8ca0","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:06:30.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me run the test to see if the tracer works. But first I need to check if there are any obvious issues with the dynamic tracer code. One issue I see: the `_get_module_qualname` method uses `frame.f_code.co_qualname` but that attribute might not exist in all Python versions. Also, the tracing might have issues with re-entrancy since we're importing the module inside the tracer context.\n\nLet me also check - when we import `temporal_attention` inside the tracer context, will the tracer intercept those imports too? Yes, but `include_external=False` means they'll be filtered out.\n\n\nI should verify that the test script is importing from the correct paths before executing it.","thinkingSignature":"88897cfda554038bb82dd9594ec28f767c6c81d671bf13429faafd69f2c74998"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lhpjtuaiunlk_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/workspace/test_tracer.py 2>&1","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54665,"output":200,"cacheRead":12619,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67484,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774220783323}}
